GPU Accelerated RGB-D SLAM with Kinect

Hardware requirements
CUDA GPU
Kinect

Software requirements
Ubuntu
ROS
openni_camera
OpenCV 2.3
PCL 1.5

Demo usage
git clone git@github.com:withniu/kinect_gpu.git
rosmake kinect_gpu --rosdep-install

# Run openni node for Kinect
rosrun kinect_gpu kinect_gpu_listener

# Use rviz to subscrible /Keypoints3d (Cloudpoint2)